12:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AIVA and Play.ht share a solid foundation of core features including . Where AIVA pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Music Generation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Play.ht uniquely offers Text To Speech and Voice Cloning and Multilingual and Api Access and Custom Voices and Real Time, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AIVA holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Play.ht scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
13:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, AIVA offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $11/mo, compared to Play.ht's starting price of $14.25/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. AIVA's free tier and Play.ht's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
